params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource name of the reseller's customer account to list entitlements for. Parent uses the format: accounts/{account_id}/customers/{customer_id}

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. Requested page size. Server might return fewer results than requested. If unspecified, return at most 50 entitlements. The maximum value is 100; the server will coerce values above 100.
